{"tid":2267168,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"伯伯入院失自理能力不能進食 瑪嘉烈男醫士細心一口一口餵食","createTime":"2020-11-02T01:18:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-02T05:41:00.000Z","uid":271829,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"0cd8f0cfc3a5bc326e73088dd5cfcf1f2cdbdf77","tid":2267168,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T01:18:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2790000/2791326/hospital_thumb_20201101_K_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2790000%2F2791326%2Fhospital_thumb_20201101_K_600.jpg&h=a2d001a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲ 年輕男護士細心為伯伯餵飯。<br />\n<br />\n本港醫療系統壓力大，但很多醫護人員不忘初心，盡力為市民提供最好的服務。最近有市民在醫院，親眼目睹一名入院的伯伯，因失去自理能力不懂自行進食，一名男護士細心一口一口餵食，餵食完後再用針筒餵水，大讚醫護人員值得表揚。<br />\n<br />\n該名市民在社交群組上發帖，並附上其拍攝的相片，從圖中可見，一名戴眼鏡的年輕男護士，細心照顧一名睡在病床上的伯伯，伯伯身體虛弱，不能動彈。該名市民表示，伯伯是從老人院送到瑪嘉烈醫院，自己不會吃飯也不善於表達，<br />\n<br />\n&quot;今天在瑪嘉烈醫院睇到一幕很值得贊掦的醫護人員，話說一位老人家從老人院送來的，不會自己吃飯也不善于表達，吃飯時間她自己也不吃，等到粥稍涼，有一位護士哥哥很有耐心的一口一口餵，老人家有時咳，有時吐出來，護士哥哥幫佢抹乾淨，再餵吃完再用針筒餵水。左右病人都說難得有這樣的醫護人員！&quot;<br />\n<br />\n該名市民更表示，伯伯有時咳嗽，將食物吐出來，護士哥哥擦乾淨後再餵食，餵完粥後再細心用針筒餵水，並指周圍的病人都大讚醫護人員的細心值得表揚。<br />\n<br />\n雖然有人留言表示，為病人餵食是護士的責任，但更多人表示香港的醫療系統壓力大，有時一名護士需要照顧多名病人，都呼籲市民與醫護人員要互相體諒。"},{"pid":"9156651c65b43ba0ebc43d66bdf98a02f199bd85","tid":2267168,"uid":90282,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T01:28:09.000Z","msg":"個個都係咁架啦"},{"pid":"285aec28a6f3ddc884ff00605ef3be23c3d9d721","tid":2267168,"uid":361751,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T01:30:45.000Z","msg":"香港做好人無用㗎<br />\n<br />\n十幾億人輪住落嚟睇醫生餵得幾多"},{"pid":"2868598b5c92d397a855938726bfc455c52fb153","tid":2267168,"uid":208511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"285aec28a6f3ddc884ff00605ef3be23c3d9d721","tid":2267168,"uid":361751,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T01:30:45.000Z","msg":"香港做好人無用㗎<br />\n<br />\n十幾億人輪住落嚟睇醫生餵得幾多"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T01:39:58.000Z","msg":"真。。。"},{"pid":"c309080e631fa98998d82825eba678875519851f","tid":2267168,"uid":28031,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T01:43:25.000Z","msg":"好咩人啫 nursing school係咁教架嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d99f54a30ed123563f3bc36373d34843aa771f4","tid":2267168,"uid":189317,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T01:49:59.000Z","msg":"張圖啲emoji咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4034afb15acf8cfaaeec7bc47e03d2d9ae2ecf3","tid":2267168,"uid":37525,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T01:57:14.000Z","msg":"啲emoji哈哈笑做乜撚？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e66f40e1eab6aa6aa6e9f63abffe53bcebf4c33e","tid":2267168,"uid":357031,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"5d99f54a30ed123563f3bc36373d34843aa771f4","tid":2267168,"uid":189317,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T01:49:59.000Z","msg":"張圖啲emoji咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T02:38:34.000Z","msg":"記者笑鳩個阿伯失去自理能力不能自行進食 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"121d241fcf6618a7016775480b231afceeea4049","tid":2267168,"uid":1082,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e66f40e1eab6aa6aa6e9f63abffe53bcebf4c33e","tid":2267168,"uid":357031,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"5d99f54a30ed123563f3bc36373d34843aa771f4","tid":2267168,"uid":189317,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T01:49:59.000Z","msg":"張圖啲emoji咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T02:38:34.000Z","msg":"記者笑鳩個阿伯失去自理能力不能自行進食 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T02:40:57.000Z","msg":"記者好黑心<i